00:00:03.960 --> 00:00:09.880
No longer the work of science-fiction, Artificial Intelligence introduces a new world and a new reality:

00:00:09.880 --> 00:00:12.580
one in which machines would be trained to think for themselves.

00:00:13.320 --> 00:00:19.080
From facial recognition and warehouse robots, to virtual assistants and autonomous vehicles,

00:00:19.080 --> 00:00:22.860
the existence of humans and machines are starting to merge.

00:00:22.860 --> 00:00:29.240
That's why the time has never been more important to consider how to create your ethical business framework for responsible AI development.

00:00:29.240 --> 00:00:31.980
This is a chief requirement for any AI strategy,

00:00:31.980 --> 00:00:34.120
and it is where we focus this course.

00:00:34.120 --> 00:00:38.680
You will learn what is driving the adoption of AI and the need for ethical frameworks,

00:00:38.680 --> 00:00:41.102
how to approach and build your company's framework,

00:00:41.102 --> 00:00:46.800
and what open source software projects are supporting the ethical advancement of these technologies.
